"Abstract Grish's Home page (www.unm.edu/at dave/) is a novel introduction to the world of security-related Web pages. Not only is it entertaining and imaginative, it is extremely useful and informative. It has links to many other valuable sites, thus acting as a conduit to numerous aspects of computer security and ethics. The site is administered by David D. Grisham, the Security Administrator of Computer and Information Resources Technology (CIRT) at the University of New Mexico."
